  <text>
     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <head>Of Hawking by the Booke.</head>
   <l>If hee that rydes, by Booke,</l>
   <l>Can make his Horse doe well:</l>
   <l>Then he, by Booke, that makes his Hawke,</l>
   <l>May make his Hawke excell.</l>
   <l>The Hawke can flee as well by Art,</l>
   <l>As Horse by rule can play his part.</l>
</div>
